      <p style=\'margin: 8px 0 0; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.4;\'>This is an automated system notification regarding your recent transaction. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>', '2026-06-26 12:55:28');
